OL,3,CTony Mowbray takes temporary step back
OL,4,Cfrom management on medical grounds
OL,6,FSunderland and Middlesbrough have sent
OL,7,Ftheir well wishes to North East
OL,8,Ffootballing giant Tony Mowbray, after
OL,9,Fit was announced he would temporarily
OL,10,Fstep back from management on medical
OL,11,Fgorunds
OL,13,FThe 60-year-old's club Birmingham City
OL,14,Fconfirmed that he would be absent for
OL,15,Fsix to eight weeks while he undergoes
OL,16,Fmedical treatment.
OL,18,FMowbray said: "Following my recent LMA
OL,19,FHealth Assessment I have received a
OL,20,Fmedical diagnosis that will require me
OL,21,Fto receive treatment.
