OL,3,CTony Mowbray takes temporary step back
OL,4,Cfrom management on medical grounds
OL,6,F"Undergoing treatment will necessitate
OL,7,Fthat I temporarily step away from the
OL,8,FTechnical Area as Manager of
OL,9,FBirmingham City Football Club.
OL,11,F"Until I return, my assistant manager,
OL,12,FMark Venus, will take temporary charge
OL,13,Fof the team, supported by coaches
OL,14,FAshley Cole, Pete Shuttleworth and
OL,15,FMaik Taylor. I will continue to
OL,16,Fprovide advice and counsel while
OL,17,Fundergoing treatment.
