OL,3,CTony Mowbray takes temporary step back
OL,4,Cfrom management on medical grounds
OL,6,F"The club has been incredibly
OL,7,Fsupportive of me and my family and we
OL,8,Fare very grateful. I know that
OL,9,Feveryone will be respectful of our
OL,10,Fprivacy at this time."
OL,12,FThe club's city chief executive
OL,13,Fofficer, Garry Cook, said: "Our
OL,14,Fthoughts are with Tony, his wife
OL,15,FAmber, and family. We wish him a
OL,16,Fspeedy recovery and look forward to
OL,17,Fwelcoming Tony back to the Club to
OL,18,Fcontinue the excellent work that he
OL,19,Fhas started.
