OL,3,CTony Mowbray takes temporary step back
OL,4,Cfrom management on medical grounds
OL,6,F"In the meantime, Mark Venus, Ashley
OL,7,FCole, Pete Shuttleworth and Maik
OL,8,FTaylor, will be given all the support
OL,9,Fthey need to lead the club forward."
OL,11,FThe former Middlesbrough captain, who
OL,12,Fwas born in Saltburn, represented the
OL,13,Fclub for nine years and returned to
OL,14,FTeesside as manager in 2010.
OL,16,FMowbray joined the Blues from
OL,17,FSunderland in January, having led the
OL,18,FBlack Cats to the Championship play-
OL,19,Foffs in their first season back in the
OL,20,Fdivision following their promotion
OL,21,Ffrom League One.
